fragment_downloaded_cb({"fragment": "Using a custom VAPI \nWhen dealing with libraries that are not providing Vala bindings a vapidir flag can be added to extend the search path for the current project. \nIn this case make sure that the VAPI name corresponds to the pkg config file. \nIf no pkg config file is provided you must use find_library. Usingdeclare_dependency is cleaner because it does not require passing both dependency objects to the target. \n", "url": "Vala.html#using-a-custom-vapi"});